            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37644350/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37644350/" class="">第171页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/72861793/" class=" " title="飘荡的果壳">飘荡的果壳</a>
                (喜欢望着天空的鱼)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
